20 Section 328.3. As used in the State Dental Act, the following
21 words, phrases, or terms, unless the context otherwise indicates,
22 shall have the following meanings:
23 1. "Accredited dental college" means an institution whose
24 dental educational program is accredited by the Commission on Dental
