4 2. "Accredited dental hygiene program" means a dental hygiene
5 educational program which is accredited by the Commission on Dental
6 Accreditation of the American Dental Association, or the Commission
7 on Dental Accreditation of Canada (CADA) or another accrediting
8 association recognized by the United States Department of Education;
9 3. "Accredited dental assisting program or class" means a
10 dental assisting program which is accredited by the Commission on
